{"tid":2025122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地稱復工率和人員返崗率接近百分百 基本上恢復正常","createTime":"2020-05-20T04:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T09:17:52.000Z","uid":166360,"like":197,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"211d62cc047cc658a327685787e72e9fc9ee0bce","tid":2025122,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"內地稱復工率和人員返崗率接近百分百 基本上恢復正常<br />\n2020-05-20 HKT 12:34<br />\n<br />\n在北京，工業和信息化部表示，內地復工率和人員返崗率接近100%，基本上恢復正常水平。<br />\n<br />\n工信部表示，上月工業主要指標有所回暖，預測第二季工業經濟運行有望回升，如果全球新型肺炎疫情受控、經濟恢復，下半年工業經濟運行狀況，可能比上半年好。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527230-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527230-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=46e39e87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527230-20200520.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d62e84a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527230-20200520.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國又贏</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd988d980c04976c8304fd20f489daeb98a682e0","tid":2025122,"uid":13308,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"無人失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653a64db3e186f60f00dcdf4317eb268cde50ee0","tid":2025122,"uid":237425,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"死左咁多人仲有得叫百份百復工率<br />\n真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"4dfbb75ffbc97431688e638dd08fc9955516691c","tid":2025122,"uid":51701,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"香港藍天到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.