即將推出的頭戴式耳機 Airpods Studio，有一部分將會是越南製造 。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，過去蘋果通常在越南廠輔助生產舊款產品。但這款Airpods Studio這是蘋果首度在越南工廠生產全新產品，將考驗蘋果在中國以外地區生產全新產品的能力。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，AirPods Studio將有兩種版本，且採用可替換的零件，便於維修和更換。此外，新型耳機還可偵測是否戴反，自動調整正確的傳送聲道。（陳俐妏／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200520/ZWKQYCSCUFL5C5E4S6SCR5TAO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200520%2FZWKQYCSCUFL5C5E4S6SCR5TAO4%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=6ec95738\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20200520%2FZWKQYCSCUFL5C5E4S6SCR5TAO4%2F&h=fed1a470\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20200520/ZWKQYCSCUFL5C5E4S6SCR5TAO4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係要呢啲.jpg</span></strong></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"332dfb86e3c57057398dde5f93b5273478f97c9f","tid":2025122,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ba15a3dedb121319ada657d6f8cc6395894abd3","tid":2025122,"uid":271545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"無返工嘅舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1759a31f14432a0a9c399d480e06d92da4f197ef","tid":2025122,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"唔代表工廠公司有單接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你可以返，但無工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65efff67e658beea28ed85c8138a56387e327e9c","tid":2025122,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"經濟回復正常！可以開始賠錢！！"},{"pid":"dcc5e4ab51ff581cc36b860bf02dbaec846c1c06","tid":2025122,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit